/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a panoramic view of a bustling street in Beijing, China. The vantage point is high, providing a bird's eye view of the scene below. The street, filled with cars and bicycles, stretches out into the distance, flanked by buildings on both sides. Power lines crisscross above, forming a network of lines against the sky. Trees line the street, their green foliage contrasting with the urban landscape. The sun shines brightly in the background, casting a warm glow over the scene. The image is slightly distorted due to the fisheye lens effect, adding a unique perspective to the photograph.
